{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji18","name":"毛泽东全集第18卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji18.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给陈毅“的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给陈毅\"的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1944年4月9日）陈毅同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来信已悉，并送少奇同志阅看。凡事忍耐，多想自己缺点，增益其所不能；照顾大局，只要不妨大的原则，多多原谅人家。忍耐最难，但作一个政治家，必须练习忍耐，这点意见，请你考虑。感冒宜多睡，少动多食。余容面叙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月九日[1]陈毅，当时任新四军代理军长，正在延安准备出席中国共产党第七"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1944,"month":4,"day":9}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":372,"page_end":372},"tags":[{"name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}